OL,3,CDriver who ignored sight warnings is
OL,4,Cjailed for killing friends
OL,6,FJones, from Blackgate Lane in Tarleton
OL,7,Fwas driving his Audi A3 when he hit
OL,8,Ffriends Marie Cunningham, 79, and
OL,9,FGrace Foulds, 85, as they crossed the
OL,10,Froad in Southport, Merseyside, on
OL,11,FNovember 30 2021.
OL,13,FHe later failed a roadside eye test.
OL,15,FBoth pensioners were taken to hospital
OL,16,Ffrom the scene in Lulworth Road, but
OL,17,Fdied in hospital from multiple
OL,18,Fcatastrophic injuries.
