OL,6,FJones was sentenced at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt to seven years and four months
OL,8,Fin jail, said Merseyside Police.
OL,10,FHe was also banned from driving for
OL,11,Fnine years and 10 months after he
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,13,Fto two counts of causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving, police added.
