OL,6,FThe court heard that Jones suffers
OL,7,Ffrom a "progressive condition",
OL,8,Fadvanced keratoconus, in both eyes
OL,9,Fwhich was "first diagnosed in excess
OL,10,Fof 10 years prior" to his most recent
OL,11,Fexamination in July 2019. Despite
OL,12,Fthis, he told Merseyside Police that
OL,13,Fhe had had his eyes tested in
OL,14,FSeptember 2021 and "there had been no
OL,15,Fissues".
