OL,7,Fthat will fill the void in the lives
OL,8,Fof the family and friends of Grace
OL,9,FFoulds and Marie Cunningham. I can
OL,10,Fonly hope that everyone affected by
OL,11,Fthis case will understand that my task
OL,12,Fis to impose a sentence in accordance
OL,13,Fwith the law.J"The sole cause of their
OL,14,Fdeaths was your dangerous driving. The
OL,15,Freason you hit them is because you
OL,16,Fsimply did not see them.J"That much is
