OL,6,F"This tragedy was unnecessary and
OL,7,Favoidable, through selfishness,
OL,8,Frecklessness, a clear disregard for
OL,9,Fthe law and the safety of others on
OL,10,Fthe road we are all here living this
OL,11,Ftrauma today."
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Andy Roper, lead
OL,14,Finvestigating officer, said: "This is
OL,15,Fan extremely sad case in which two
OL,16,Fwomen lost their lives and our
OL,17,Fthoughts, sympathies and support very
OL,18,Fmuch remain with both families."
